– Added some trailers

Features:
– Standalone truck
– 3 Cabins
– 3 Chassis
– 4 Engine with Own Sounds
– 2 Interiors each chassis
– 3 Transmissions with retarder
– DLC Cabin Support
– Cable simulation
– Tuning Parts



How to install ETS2 mods or ATS Mods

In Euro Truck Simulator 2 it’s easy to install mods. You just need to download mod from here, copy/unzip files into: “My Documents\Euro Truck Simulator 2\mod” folder or if you play ATS please install mods to: “My Documents\American Truck Simulator\mod” folder. To unzip files you can use: WinRAR or 7zip. After that you need to activate the mods you want to use.

item.title: Map of Southeast Asia v0.2.5.1 1.50 ETS2
item.description:
Map of Southeast Asia v0.2.5.1 1.50 ETS2

UPDATE:
New Country: Laos
Added a copy of ios for map exploration
Added a new map overlap
Added new flags
New AI: Motorcycle
Added 13 new cities and towns
Replaced some planes on the map
Added some billboards
Added fixes with Road To Asia
Changed flags and added some new flags (thanks to Septian for creating the flags)
Thanks to imxiaoanag for helping us temporarily fix a license plate issue that could be causing the crash.

DESCRIPTION:
8 countries (Myanmar, Thailand, Malaysia, Singapore, Philippines, Vietnam, Papua New Guinea, Laos)
Can be used in combination with Promods, JRR, Rusmap, MAPA EAA, Southern Region, Kazakhstan, Siberia, Road to Asia and others maps
Requires all DLC maps to work
It is highly desirable to have a background map that includes Asia (otherwise you will not see this map)
In the future, the remaining areas of southern Thailand, central and northern Thailand, Laos, Cambodia, Brunei, the east coast of Peninsular Malaysia, East Malaysia will appear (Sabah and Sarawak), Myanmar, Vietnam, Philippines, East Timor, Bangladesh and other regions
